			<div class="content" id="post-content-1497398">
									

<p>Actually, it would explain some of what happened in that tale:</p>
<blockquote>
<p>&quot;682?&quot; 343 called out, a brief flash of anger in his eyes. Between one moment and the next he is standing in front of me, somehow taller than me without changing his size, glaring down at me. &quot;You brought me to 682?&quot; I motioned behind his back at English, who quickly began the 682 containment procedures, flooding the room with acid.</p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>&quot;Sure did, 343. Got a problem with that?&quot; Anger, from God. With luck, he'd off me, and I wouldn't have to go through with the second part of this test.</p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>Instead, 343 simply turned his back on me. &quot;He's not one of mine. Deal with him yourself.&quot; And stalked off through the wall.</p>
</blockquote>
<p>He remembered what 682 did, and is still pissed he ate the Ark.</p>
<p>(I know, I know, but it <strong>does</strong> kind of make sense!)</p>

