			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1497417">
									

<p>Not really, that scene displays that 343 isn't pissed because 682 did something, he's pissed because <em>something</em> else created it. Think of it like 343 is an artist, he created our whatever and all was jolly for him, then someone went a head and slapped a big ugly blob of ink onto his painting. They ruined his hand crafted piece of art and he hates it, he hates that ugly ink blob and he despises that other artist.</p>
<p>The question isn't &quot;what did 682 do?&quot; it's &quot;who made 682?&quot;</p>

