			<div class="content" id="post-content-3585748">
									

<p>Noting that I have removed the tag '682'. To my knowledge, SCPs don't get their own tags. If one wants to propose to have a '682' tag, please do it officially via the <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/forum/t-2219013/tag-suggestion-thread">Tag Suggestion Thread</a>, instead of adding it in.</p>
<p>After all, if there is only just one article with that particular tag, is it even performing its duty as a tag?</p>

